text: Nosherwan Khan (born 11 June 1994 in Peshawar) is a Pakistani professional squash player. As of March 2018, he was ranked number 333 in the world. He has competed in the main draw of multiple professional PSA tournaments.http://www.squashsite.co.uk/2009/karachiinternational13.htmhttp://www.squashinfo.com/events/7133-mens- mid-atlantic-pro-classic-2017 ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani male squash players
